00:57:42,560 --> 00:57:45,677
Hey, Mario, how about this?
Your mother did.

650
00:57:45,800 --> 00:57:49,429
Don't you ever say anything,
ever, about my mother.

651
00:57:49,560 --> 00:57:52,199
Your mother did, your mother did. Mario!

652
00:57:54,200 --> 00:57:57,033
- How do we handle this?
- Just pull over.

